 * /guides/faut-il-des-batteries, synced to the fact-corrected FR (LFP cost,
 * buy-back vs purchase spread, payback). Figures mirror the FR 1:1 — no new
 * claim. Internal links use localizeNavHref (EN/AR if available, else the
 * existing FR page — never a dead link). FR untouched.
